<h4 class="wp-block-heading">How To Do</h4>



<ol>
<li>Start by standing with your feet together and arms at your sides.</li>



<li>Jump your feet out to the sides while bringing your arms above your head.</li>



<li>Explosively jump back to the starting position.</li>



<li>Repeat for the desired number of repetitions, or check the table below.</li>
</ol>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Tips</h4>



<ul>
<li>Land softly on the balls of your feet to reduce the impact on your joints.</li>



<li>Keep your core engaged throughout the movement for balance and stability.</li>



<li>Maintain a steady rhythm for maximum cardiovascular benefit.</li>



<li>If needed, start with half jacks (legs only) and progress to full jumping jacks.</li>
</ul>



